init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and the bee says "I'm not a bee, I'm your guardian angel.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm here to tell you that you're not allergic, it was a lie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You know that if you call your mother, she'll be mad at the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee just says "To protect you."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You don't understand and the bee explains "You're a princess.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Now you are free, but it means things will change.
